│ - Extend DenseMapInfo<ScalarEvolution::SCEVCallbackVH> with alt-key support: getHashValue(Value*) and isEqual(KeyT, Value*) so find_as can avoid constructing a             │
│ SCEVCallbackVH from a Value*.                                                                                                                                               │
